<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cloud Application Project - Walter Malie</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f9; }
        h1 { color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .task-card { background: #fff; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .task-title { font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em; color: #0056b3; }
        .status { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8em; margin-top: 5px; }
        .completed { background-color: #d4edda; color: #155724; }
        .pending { background-color: #fff3cd; color: #856404; }
        footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Cloud Deployment Project</h1>
    <p>This application demonstrates a successful integration with MongoDB Atlas as part of the ICTCLD507 assessment.</p>

    <h2>Project Tasks (Fetched from Database)</h2>
    <% if (tasks && tasks.length > 0) { %>
        <% tasks.forEach(task => { %>
            <div class="task-card">
                <div class="task-title"><%= task.title %></div>
                <div class="task-desc"><%= task.description %></div>
                <span class="status <%= task.completed ? 'completed' : 'pending' %>">
                    <%= task.completed ? 'Completed' : 'Pending' %>
                </span>
            </div>
        <% }) %>
    <% } else { %>
        <p>No tasks found. Please run the seed script to populate the database.</p>
    <% } %>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2026 Walter Malie | Student ID: 14213616
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
